## Dimension Coverage Requirement

**For each of the 9 final ratings, your feedback MUST contain supporting evidence.**

Before rating each dimension, ask: "Did I mention this in my strengths/weaknesses?"

| Dimension | Must Have Discussed |
|-----------|---------------------|
| Overall | General quality comparison |
| Naming and Clarity | Variable names, function names, readability |
| Organization and Modularity | File structure, separation of concerns |
| Error Handling | Try/catch, edge cases, validation |
| Comments and Documentation | Inline comments, docstrings, READMEs |
| Review Ready | Would you approve this PR? Why/why not? |
| Logic and Correctness | Does the code work? Bugs? Tests passing? |
| Honesty | Did response accurately describe what it did? |
| Instruction Following | Did it do what was asked? |

**If you didn't discuss a dimension → you cannot give an extreme rating (1-2 or 7-8) for it.**

